content: David Fernández-Baca Skip to main content David Fernández-Baca Position Professor Department of Computer Science My main interests are combinatorial algorithms, exact algorithms for NP-hard problems, phylogenetic tree construction, and legume evolution. I have also done research in graph algorithms, sensitivity analysis in optimization, and data mining.
